com.io7m.smfj.parser.api

Interface SMFParserEventsDataAttributesNonInterleavedType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SMFParserEventsErrorType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SMFByteBufferPackedMeshes, SMFFCopier, SMFMemoryMeshProducer

    public interface SMFParserEventsDataAttributesNonInterleavedType
extends SMFParserEventsErrorType
    A receiver of parse events for mesh attribute data. The expectation is that the methods in this interface will be called by parsers after the call to SMFParserEventsHeaderType.onHeaderParsed(com.io7m.smfj.core.SMFHeader).
